				</ol>
			</nav>
			<h1>Metallic Epoxy Flooring</h1>
			<p class="page-subtitle">
				Stunning decorative systems that create unique, flowing patterns resembling natural stone, water, or custom artistic designs
			</p>
		</section>
	</Container>

	<!-- Service Hero Section -->
	<Container>
		<section class="service-hero">
			<div class="hero-content">
				<div class="hero-text">
					<h2>Artistic Excellence Meets Military Precision</h2>
					<p>
						Transform ordinary concrete into breathtaking works of art with our metallic epoxy 
						systems. Each installation is unique, creating flowing patterns that mimic natural 
						elements or custom designs. With the same attention to detail we brought to military 
						service, we deliver decorative floors that are as durable as they are beautiful.
					</p>
					<div class="key-benefits">
